snippet.title: New Rivals of Aether Assist in Fraymakers!
snippet.description:
Wishlist Fraymakers on Steam: http://www.fraymakers.com/steam

Our trailer that aired during Rivals Direct 4, featuring the results of our Rivals of Aether assist poll and the fourth confirmed character for Early Access launch! 

Follow us for Fraymakers updates: 
• Twitter: https://twitter.com/FraymakersGame
• Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fraymakersgame/

The full version of Fighter Select will be posted here tomorrow!

Cover by the Super Soul Bros. - https://www.supersoulbros.com

Original composition by flashygoodness - https://flashygoodness.bandcamp.com

#fraymakers #indie #rivalsofaether
